# .strathon-forbidden-words.example
#
# Copy this file to .strathon-forbidden-words and add your org-specific
# patterns. One regex pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# The pre-commit hook (scripts/check-secrets.sh) will block commits
# containing any of these patterns in code files (not docs).
#
# Example patterns:
# CompetitorName
# InternalProjectCode
# internal-only-domain\.com
